0/1.8<br />\n一支影出黎<br />\n相對難用<br />\n但又好好<br />\n黎梗自己去旅行<br />\n都諗梗好冇簡單少少</blockquote><br />\n去旅行去既地方一般都唔係成日可以去到<br />\n如果到時有idea係要用wide/ tele先實現到<br />\n但你得支50就影唔到果個shot了<br />\n<br />\n當然，就算得支定焦都無話影唔到靚相</blockquote><br />\n真心想知，咩tele先影到</blockquote><br />\n其實好多風景相都係tele影架喎</blockquote><br />\n留名學野，不嬲都手動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40a576a673ab120e62d6c473abb9f9593be0355","tid":435460,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時都覺得太多焦距影得反而唔專心<br />\n<br />\n攪到啲相好到此一遊feel<br />\n<br />\n當然自己都唔係影得叻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上次睇連登一個日本遊記<br />\n<br />\n冇記錯絲打黎<br />\n<br />\n用apsc配50/1.8<br />\n<br />\n一支影出黎<br />\n<br />\n相對難用<br />\n<br />\n但又好好<br />\n<br />\n黎梗自己去旅行<br />\n<br />\n都諗梗好冇簡單少少</blockquote><br />\n華麗現身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc455c96fbb886463039d7bae84f783c8a43a709","tid":435460,"uid":44377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有時都覺得太多焦距影得反而唔專心<br />\n攪到啲相好到此一遊feel<br />\n當然自己都唔係影得叻<br />\n<br />\n上次睇連登一個日本遊記<br />\n冇記錯絲打黎<br />\n用apsc配50/1.8<br />\n一支影出黎<br />\n相對難用<br />\n但又好好<br />\n黎梗自己去旅行<br />\n都諗梗好冇簡單少少</blockquote><br />\n去旅行去既地方一般都唔係成日可以去到<br />\n如果到時有idea係要用wide/ tele先實現到<br />\n但你得支50就影唔到果個shot了<br />\n<br />\n當然，就算得支定焦都無話影唔到靚相</blockquote><br />\n真心想知，咩tele先影到</blockquote><br />\n其實好多風景相都係tele影架喎</blockquote><br />\n留名學野，不嬲都手動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手動同tele有咩關係<br />\n例如呢D, 大部份都係tele影出黎<br />\n呢個tour玩tele影風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://czech.photos/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fczech.photos%2F&d=xl8qb1EPxtlhBa4j0EbLgr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f489a575\" target=\"_blank\">http://czech.photos/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://czech.photos/grafika/south-moravia-fields2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fczech.photos%2Fgrafika%2Fsouth-moravia-fields2.jpg&h=c639e727&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2277b3885bfb8ac930abfbdf01d7aaab1f774245","tid":435460,"uid":78252,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T07:01:32.000Z","msg":"分享下經驗<br />\n帶廣角 帶定焦去 影出黎會有唔會既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果真係要剩帶一支，睇你重視邊樣多d<br />\n<br />\n大景撚，廣角是必備的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去到d觀景台/一條橋、山邊呢d有限空間上，你拎住50mm唔係幾時都可以行後幾十步去取得10mm既景<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/24/143100_855e96ac722a6cdb4258bcd5a8132618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F24%2F143100_855e96ac722a6cdb4258bcd5a8132618.jpg&h=39326f79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/24/143102_e61ef47106c9c3a8d53cf66a02649eb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F24%2F143102_e61ef47106c9c3a8d53cf66a02649eb3.jpg&h=df035302&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/24/143108_d090fcbfee65f6cafe397f84a50eeb5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F24%2F143108_d090fcbfee65f6cafe397f84a50eeb5b.jpg&h=319b17f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/24/143110_a4c38f095e609f1f0b965b1e4251c3ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F24%2F143110_a4c38f095e609f1f0b965b1e4251c3ad.jpg&h=95194fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/24/143111_ab14a22ecf08e350bc538e2d42a15f27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F24%2F143111_ab14a22ecf08e350bc538e2d42a15f27.jpg&h=e9481126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且（個人觀感）個環境既線條都有所影響，較有置身其中既感覺<br />\n<img src=\"https://mangotofufa.files.wordpress.com/2017/05/img_7660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmangotofufa.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F05%2Fimg_7660.jpg&h=8d5d1752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但對大景無興趣，想影人像/男女神相、街拍為主，定焦就夠做<br />\n<br />\n我試過剩帶40 2.8，<br />\n試過 剩帶10-18 ，<br />\n試過兩支都帶，<br />\n試過10-18 加18- 135<br />\n<br />\n而我最常做法係帶曬頭兩支，不過主要都只會用10-18，原因係我係鐘意影大景、landscape、建築全貌，景點撚黎，但當影人影食物就會想有定焦鏡，因為得出黎既感覺會好唔同，用10-18影人+景，較容易得出中坑到此一遊既遊行相，無咩特別，或者我技術差，好彩40 2.8輕到傻，用2.8影出黎，影人、食物會有feel d，因為有d景深<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ylJeFBg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FylJeFBg.jpg&h=016dffa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Yadu9Ym.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYadu9Ym.jpg&h=6cc4355f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/z5GIfNb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fz5GIfNb.jpg&h=00b305b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我試過剩帶40 2.8影景（因為去第二次，影過廣角相，先敢剩帶40）<br />\n唔會影唔到相既，但主題可能唔同，唔再係大環境，而係focus其中一間屋之類，感覺係唔同既<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/pMg817o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpMg817o.jpg&h=8923db6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/QWs8jjY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQWs8jjY.jpg&h=d945d5db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://mangotofufa.files.wordpress.com/2017/04/img_7606-e1491221184468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmangotofufa.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F04%2Fimg_7606-e1491221184468.jpg&h=4e811393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NzJYd1P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNzJYd1P.jpg&h=f46ac794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KxC21SE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKxC21SE.jpg&h=e73aec3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/q1X3paO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq1X3paO.jpg&h=f8b8e762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一樣係影到風景<br />\n但會有d限制<br />\n但影人果d相就相當滿意（個trip主要幫家姐影相留念下）<br />\n<br />\n所以都係睇你自己想影邊類相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3b7b5367485eaac5f11206bac02430db7df9ee","tid":435460,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T07:10:27.000Z","msg":"其實係講緊唔需要TELE, 因為可以CROP?<br />\n咁通常TELE都係拎個壓縮感既, 例如拉近D山脈<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn3.craftsy.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/sunrise_layers_boott_spur_4809.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn3.craftsy.com%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F01%2Fsunrise_layers_boott_spur_4809.jpg&h=e47f8e12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6765e23e0950e49e374f78c8e190e33c1863eb6","tid":435460,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有時都覺得太多焦距影得反而唔專心<br />\n攪到啲相好到此一遊feel<br />\n當然自己都唔係影得叻<br />\n<br />\n上次睇連登一個日本遊記<br />\n冇記錯絲打黎<br />\n用apsc配50/1.8<br />\n一支影出黎<br />\n相對難用<br />\n但又好好<br />\n黎梗自己去旅行<br />\n都諗梗好冇簡單少少</blockquote><br />\n去旅行去既地方一般都唔係成日可以去到<br />\n如果到時有idea係要用wide/ tele先實現到<br />\n但你得支50就影唔到果個shot了<br />\n<br />\n當然，就算得支定焦都無話影唔到靚相</blockquote><br />\n真心想知，咩tele先影到</blockquote><br />\n其實好多風景相都係tele影架喎</blockquote><br />\n留名學野，不嬲都手動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手動同tele有咩關係<br />\n例如呢D, 大部份都係tele影出黎<br />\n呢個tour玩tele影風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://czech.photos/\" data-sr-url=\"https://